---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import TerminalPanel from '../components/TerminalPanel.astro';
import CommandButton from '../components/CommandButton.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Revenue Systems Architect focused on AI-native RevOps and GTM automation.">
  <article class="py-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-4">
        About
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_300px] lg:gap-8">
      <!-- Main content -->
      <div class="space-y-8 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text)]">
          Revenue Systems Architect building AI-native RevOps that stays reliable in production.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-label)] uppercase tracking-wide">Guiding principles</div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <p class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Governed data beats clever automation.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
                <li>Evidence: Unified lifecycle, stage, and attribution definitions across CRM and warehouse.</li>
                <li>Implication: Forecasts and pipeline reporting stay reliable.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <p class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Automation should shorten response time without hiding errors.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
                <li>Evidence: Built enrichment, routing, and SLA workflows with monitoring and human checkpoints.</li>
                <li>Implication: Teams spend time on selling and insight, not cleanup.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <p class="text-[var(--color-text)]">RevOps systems need end-to-end ownership.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
                <li>Evidence: 10+ years across sales, GTM, and data; led AI-enabled GTM ops since 2022.</li>
                <li>Implication: Faster launches with clear accountability and adoption.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-label)] uppercase tracking-wide">Selected outcomes</div>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
            <li>Generated $8M+ in qualified pipeline leading the enterprise team at Benchling.</li>
            <li>Drove ~40% pipeline growth with AWS channel enablement at CloudZero.</li>
            <li>Ranked top 10% at DataRobot, producing ~$350K/month pipeline.</li>
            <li>Delivered $200K+ pipeline and ~$75K average monthly ARR at Smartsheet.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-label)] uppercase tracking-wide">Selected roles</div>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
            <li>2022 to Present - Revenue Systems Architect (Freelance) - AI-enabled GTM ops and automation.</li>
            <li>2021 to 2022 - Benchling - Global Lead, Enterprise Development.</li>
            <li>2020 to 2021 - CloudZero - Cloud Cost Solutions Enablement.</li>
            <li>2019 to 2020 - DataRobot - AI Solutions Specialist.</li>
            <li>2018 to 2019 - Smartsheet - Sales Development.</li>
            <li>Earlier: UMass Amherst - Software Support and Network Engineering.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-label)] uppercase tracking-wide">Systems delivered</div>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
            <li>Lead routing and enrichment automations in Salesforce and HubSpot.</li>
            <li>Data models in Snowflake and dbt for pipeline and attribution.</li>
            <li>Executive reporting layers in Looker, Tableau, and Power BI.</li>
            <li>AI workflows with validation, monitoring, and human checkpoints.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Resume section -->
        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-4">
            Full career history on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/julianross21/" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
          </p>
          <CommandButton
            href="/julian-ross-resume.pdf"
            command="Download resume"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="hidden lg:block">
        <TerminalPanel title="Snapshot">
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
            <li><span class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Experience:</span> 10+ years across GTM + RevOps</li>
            <li><span class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Focus:</span> AI-native revenue systems</li>
            <li><span class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Specialty:</span> RevOps, agentic workflows, GTM automation</li>
          </ul>
        </TerminalPanel>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
